sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Flask-RESTX API
    participant DB as SQLite Database

    Player->>Frontend: Finish game
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/v1/scores
    API->>API: Validate game_id and score
    API->>DB: Save score
    API->>DB: Query top 10 leaderboard
    API->>DB: Query player personal rank
    DB-->>API: Return leaderboard data
    API-->>Frontend: Return top 10 and player rank
    Frontend-->>Player: Display updated leaderboard
